#: templates/public/about.html:80
msgid "About Weilight Harbor"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:81
msgid ""
"A warm digital harbor for caregivers and families navigating the journey "
"of serious illness. Here, no one walks alone."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:89
msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:91
msgid ""
"Weilight Harbor was born from a simple belief: caregivers and families "
"facing serious illness deserve a safe space to share, connect, and find "
"support. We provide a platform where empathy flows freely, where stories "
"illuminate the path for others, and where practical help is always within"
" reach."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:101
msgid "Our Values"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:108
msgid "Compassion"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:109
msgid ""
"Every interaction is grounded in empathy and understanding. We listen "
"without judgment and support without conditions."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:117
msgid "Safety"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:118
msgid ""
"This is a safe harbor. We protect privacy, moderate content sensitively, "
"and maintain a space free from harm."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:127
msgid ""
"Strength comes from connection. We bring together families, volunteers, "
"and organizations to form a caring community."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:139 templates/public/index.html:53
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:143
msgid "Create an Account"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:144
msgid ""
"Sign up for free and join our community. Optionally get certified to "
"unlock more features."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:150
msgid "Connect and Share"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:151
msgid ""
"Share your story in the community, keep a private life journal, or find "
"support at the respite station."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:157
msgid "Give and Receive Help"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:158
msgid ""
"Launch or support crowdfunding campaigns, volunteer your time, or simply "
"be there for someone who needs it."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:171
msgid "Our Team"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/about.html:173
msgid ""
"Weilight Harbor is built by a small team of designers, developers, and "
"social workers who have been personally touched by the caregiving "
"journey. We understand the challenges because we have lived them. Every "
"feature is crafted with real needs in mind."
msgstr ""

