#: templates/public/help.html:88
msgid "How do I create an account?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:93
msgid ""
"Click \"Join the Harbor\" in the top navigation bar. Fill in your "
"username, email, and password. After registration, you will be "
"automatically logged in and can start using all basic features right "
"away."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:100
msgid "What is certification and do I need it?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:105
msgid ""
"Certification verifies your identity as a family caregiver or volunteer. "
"While not required for basic features like browsing and posting, "
"certification unlocks advanced features such as creating crowdfunding "
"campaigns and builds trust within the community. You can apply from your "
"profile page."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:112
msgid "Is the platform free to use?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:117
msgid ""
"Yes, Weilight Harbor is completely free for all users. We are a non-"
"profit platform dedicated to helping caregivers and families. All "
"donations through crowdfunding go directly to the campaign recipients."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:132
msgid "How do I create a post?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:137
msgid ""
"Navigate to the Community page and click \"Create Post.\" You can share "
"your experiences, ask questions, or offer support. Posts are moderated to"
" keep the community safe and respectful."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:144
msgid "Can I post anonymously?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:149
msgid ""
"Yes, you can choose to post anonymously when creating a post. Anonymous "
"posts will show a generic username to protect your privacy while still "
"allowing you to share and connect."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:164
msgid "How do I start a crowdfunding campaign?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:169
msgid ""
"You need to be a certified user to create a campaign. Once certified, go "
"to the Crowdfunding page and click \"Create Campaign.\" Fill in the "
"details about the patient, the funding goal, and your story. Campaigns "
"are reviewed before going live."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:176
msgid "How are funds distributed?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:181
msgid ""
"This is a demo platform. In a production environment, funds would be "
"transferred directly to the verified recipient after the campaign ends or"
" when withdrawal is requested. All transactions would be transparent and "
"auditable."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:190
msgid "Account & Privacy"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:196
msgid "How is my personal information protected?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:201
msgid ""
"We take privacy seriously. Personal information submitted during "
"certification is encrypted and only accessible to authorized reviewers. "
"We never share your data with third parties. See our Privacy Policy for "
"full details."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:208
msgid "How do I reset my password?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:213
msgid ""
"Click \"Forgot password?\" on the login page and enter your registered "
"email address. You will receive a password reset link. Note: this is a "
"demo feature in the current version."
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:222
msgid "Still need help?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/public/help.html:223
msgid ""
"If you could not find an answer to your question, feel free to reach out "
"to our support team."
msgstr ""

